## Integration Notes

- This service handles ALL file attachments across ZoneVast
- Attachments are multi-tenant: filtered by `tenant_project_id`
- CloudFront (`file.zonevast.com`) serves files publicly after upload
- Content deduplication: send `file_hash` (SHA-256) with presigned URL request
- Auth uses `JWTAuthenticationWithoutDB` (no DB lookup per request in Lambda)
